"okem pa k'amaya'l, akuchi' ye'atz'aqatisaj k'ak'a' taq samaj pa Firefox, nawutzilaj ri ak'exb'anik rik'in ri Ajk'amaya'l etamab'äl chuqa' najalwachij ruwäch ri awokik'amaya'l."

